    https://salsa.debian.org/jelmer/debian-janitor/-/issues/138
  * Fix branch from vcswatch in --diligent mode.
  * apply-multiarch-hints: fix Changes-by field.
  * debianize: Make breezy-debian optional.
  * Add debianize(1) manpage.

